\begin{abstract}
This paper is devoted to the study of vector valued reproducing
kernel Hilbert spaces. We focus on reproducing kernels in vector-valued reproducing kernel Hilbert spaces.
In particular we extend reproducing kernels to relative reproducing kernels and prove some theorems in this subject.
\end{abstract}


